title: Call.Of.Duty.Modern.Warfare.2.Complete.Edition-DiGiTALZONE
description:
Call Of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 Complete Edition [DiGiTALZONE]
Includes: ALL DLC Packs, Singleplayer, Multiplayer

The most-anticipated game of the year and the sequel to the best-selling first-person action game of all time, Modern Warfare 2 continues the gripping and heart-racing action as players face off against a new threat dedicated to bringing the world to the brink of collapse. 

Features:

- Original content with latest updates, nothing ripped
- Singleplayer works
- Multiplayer works, Internet and LAN (offline too)
- Spec Ops works, both Solo and Co-op over Internet/LAN*
- ReactIW4 version r415 (does not require a master server)
- Compatible with mods
- Dedicated server included
- Clean install with no unneeded files

*NOTE: Two Player Spec Ops has no server browser, you must join via console by typing: connect <IP:PORT>

Extras:

- DLC: Stimulus Package - 5 new maps
  * Crash
  * Overgrown
  * Bailout
  * Salvage
  * Storm

- DLC: Resurgence Pack - 5 new maps
  * Carnival
  * Fuel
  * Trailer Park
  * Strike
  * Vacant

- MAP: Nuketown from Call Of Duty: Black Ops

- DLC: Classics #1 Pack - 3 maps from Call Of Duty 4: Modern Warfare
  * Bloc
  * Wetwork
  * Crossfire

- DLC: Classics #2 Pack - 2 maps from Call Of Duty 4: Modern Warfare
  * Bog
  * Killhouse

- New Weapons Pack - 4 new weapons
  * AK-74u Submachine Gun
  * Peacekeeper Submachine Gun
  * M40A3 Sniper Rifle
  * MK-14 Enhanced Battle Rifle

- New Gamemodes Pack - 11 new entertaining game modes
  * Arena		* One Flag CTF	* Global Thermonuclear War  
  * Cranked	* Kill Confirmed	* VIP
  * Gun Game	* Team Defender	* One in the Chamber
  * Infected	* Sharpshooter
